fn_tests.input_infer:
""          // edge case: empty string, should not panic but return valid HeaderValue
"hello"     // valid input, should return HeaderValue without panic
"hello\x7f" // input with a non-visible ASCII character, should panic
"hello\x1f" // input with a non-visible ASCII character, should panic
"hello ват"  // input with a non-visible ASCII character (non-ASCII), should panic
"valid\t"    // input with tab character, should return HeaderValue without panic
" "          // input with a space, valid case, should return HeaderValue without panic
